reviewText: Bought for my Spanish classroom. Not appropriate:-( The mothers sex toy innuendos & there is a sex scene, otherwise it would have been perfect!
muy amena y graciosa llego bien y en buen estado.

The Mayan Riviera is definitely the star of this movie. The scenery, the photography and the beauty of Mexico make this predictable romantic film something worth watching. Forget the story, just allow yourself to get caught up in planning a trip to Mexico!!
I like this movie because of the sites of Riviera Maya in Mexico, this is a wonderful way to get the idea of how beautiful this place is!
